{"type": "article", "id": 18242, "title": "Signature Chair", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-30T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110611rnoQbyAX8aEYW5Jd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tFrits Henningsen 是丹麦的木匠，这把带有古典主义风格的椅子设计于 1952 年，灵感源于橡皮泥和牙签，有宽大柔和的曲线靠背和细长轻盈的木质结构，很优雅。丹麦的家具品牌 Carl Hansen &amp; Søn 近日将这把椅子生产出来，使用橡木做结构，得以让扶手和椅腿保留曲线感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110608ln6yI8jWRNxDVgqS.jpg\" width=\"937\" height=\"782\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83457844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021106091tQPNlZS5hUTFEbk.jpg\" width=\"935\" height=\"894\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95614973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110610E9pVayl1mdjviUAg.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110610MlCwvziZXEReybh8.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}